---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import EmailSignup from '../components/EmailSignup.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="About Murmmers Press: an independent publisher of fiction with a healing element.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>A small press you can trust</h1>

      <p>Murmmers Press is an independent publisher of fiction with a healing element. We publish quiet, characterful books and bring each one to the world with its own voice intact.</p>

      <h2>The work</h2>
      <p>Every book is edited to protect what makes it itself, never to smooth it into sameness. We correct and tighten what is on the page. We do not regenerate it. Where a book is best read in one sitting, we treat that as a gift to the reader, not a shortfall.</p>

      <h2>The author</h2>
      <p>The founding list is the work of Eric McLean, who directs the press. More voices will follow as the catalogue grows.</p>

      <h2>The spirit</h2>
      <p>We believe attention is a kind of care, and that a book held with attention can hold you back. That is the whole of it.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem">
        <EmailSignup />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
